# Set the seed for the random number generator so you will get the same results
  set.seed(1207) 

  data <- rnorm_multi(
    n = 500,          
    mu = c(0, 1),   
    sd = c(1, 1),   
    r = c(0.5), 
    varnames = c("x", "y"),
    empirical = FALSE
    )
  data |>
  ggplot(aes(x = x, y = y)) +
    geom_point(color = col4)

  m1 <- lm(y ~ x, data = data)
